提係我地輸打贏要。贏左先當公投，輸左就要discredit個選舉。煲大禁止查冊，煲大選舉舞弊，一定要外媒都知。咁樣我哋輸左票數都唔會失去太多海外支持。唔少外媒以為今次係公投，非常危險，必須糾正，否則萬劫不復。<br />\n<br />\n記住一定要投票，但係上面兩項同樣重要。"},{"pid":"8e55fb6edb82ff663edbe0d5e1f73706e8bd9c3b","tid":1746541,"uid":277944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0c59a6e724d695f346c83541c3c7dbfc8fc3d89","tid":1746541,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:17:03.000Z","msg":"相等於政府/黑警獲得民意授權<br />\n之後黑警既鎮壓會更加不人道同無後果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:19:05.000Z","msg":"同意民意是很重要<br />\n但對家又種票又做手腳<br />\n同真正民意會有差別"},{"pid":"0b1886fff7a804447222b2493dd7741ec41b1a5e","tid":1746541,"uid":310461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b742d1d3934d7ffb8d9ce791c7d9e7f62757ee04","tid":1746541,"uid":58104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T19:17:38.000Z","msg":"無論你地承唔承認 今次區選都係一個公投"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:24:31.000Z","msg":"It is a 公投!!!<br />\n<br />\nEXTREMELY important  !!!<br />\n<br />\nCCP and BlueC have started very early and put in lots of effort to push votes!!!<br />\n<br />\nCannot lose !!<br />\n<br />\nWork HARD !!!"},{"pid":"4b74307396d8597355ee344d99c9b64281a7ff15","tid":1746541,"uid":269934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f358cb31a60fde474a50b16107d63c0b95d282d7","tid":1746541,"uid":236140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T20:20:12.000Z","msg":"手足做啲乜嘢和理非都唔會割蓆<br />\n<br />\n和理非要求好簡單，就係要建制派輸 <br />\n<br />\n各位手足，幫幫手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T22:25:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f244e4f5a907dae1eb6ce54a38e3c44b6899709","tid":1746541,"uid":310461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T00:30:43.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<span